{"tid":540521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班輔警涉巴士與人互毆 雙雙被捕","createTime":"2018-01-25T14:44:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T15:54:53.000Z","uid":5195,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"844c663e70f7cfce09b9ab252cf739be62003537","tid":540521,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T14:44:58.000Z","msg":"休班輔警涉嫌於巴士上與人打架，雙方同被捕。昨晚10時許，一名姓李(35歲)男子與一名姓黃(26歲)休班警同乘一輛由紅磡區駛往觀塘區的巴士，期間雙方因瑣事爭執，涉嫌互相襲擊對方，巴士抵黃大仙景泰街巴士站時，黃報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李手、眼及鼻受傷，黃則面部受傷，由救護員送院治療，2人送院時清醒。警方經初步調查後，以涉嫌在公眾地方打架將李與黃拘捕，案件交由黃大仙警區重案組第1隊跟進。目前兩人俱已獲准保釋候查，須於下月上旬向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。"},{"pid":"41ec9cd1e321fa49f745041c47527acbdaf0a65c","tid":540521,"uid":33481,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T14:45:46.000Z","msg":"警方指，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。"},{"pid":"c1d4e39a4c7f89c954ce51a7a2795560d96b59da","tid":540521,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T14:46:52.000Z","msg":"休班輔警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0996c39c55c1d27a6f52999bde90599bce86062","tid":540521,"uid":89478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1d4e39a4c7f89c954ce51a7a2795560d96b59da","tid":540521,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T14:46:52.000Z","msg":"休班輔警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T14:59:33.000Z","msg":"一個係警 另一個係律師又唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96763d164da04f4abab991c368235554b0671b5","tid":540521,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T15:01:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>休班輔警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>一個係警 另一個係律師又唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n律師 食住 警察 食住 市民"},{"pid":"d7d6f2f151b753c6d9401674d21a3a135437b3dd","tid":540521,"uid":36543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T15:14:24.000Z","msg":"唔係應該告返果條友襲警咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a78fc6d0f136ed92717e0fbeafca640bc72781","tid":540521,"uid":89478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e96763d164da04f4abab991c368235554b0671b5","tid":540521,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T15:01:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>休班輔警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>一個係警 另一個係律師又唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n律師 食住 警察 食住 市民"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T15:46:17.000Z","msg":"啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 市民食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b64a2ba5a71da63d2024321b78dd38da9a02c77","tid":540521,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T15:54:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}